Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:23.86,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}斷裂的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是今天  赤夜不出現的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的可以嗎  一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩子的工資  就是大家的工資
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也畢竟難得  我就不客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵  多吃點  多吃點  吃個一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉  好久沒吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  彩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩…子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩…彩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩子  振作點  彩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我  彩子  彩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栞同學  你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑騎士的同夥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試探了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你順利地…不  驚人地成長了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做為我們能托付希望的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你們的羈絆全都扯斷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了啊  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  因威迪亞抱著自爆的覺悟突擊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺  殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了  我的毀滅之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人拼死要殺掉我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是考驗我們的團結之時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是團隊被打亂的話就會直接帶來死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火災？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你呢  去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這模樣  出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那能力打倒惡魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒惡魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒惡魔的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且能打倒惡魔的也只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢栞同學  說要我打倒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了  這屋子已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是  斯佩爾比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫之眼的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是赤夜  為什麼你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要消耗生命力我們也能穿梭兩個世界  僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師被殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  這種事實在是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  明明不是赤夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼斯佩爾比亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  現在應該面對現實  迅速解決事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久前輩因為憤怒和悲傷過度  失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須盡快打倒斯佩爾比亞  阻止賢久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁那丫頭不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把她叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…斯佩爾比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的  這強大的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那賢久前輩是在跟誰戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子  賢久的事就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和菊理去找斯佩爾比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先行一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事有蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心裡的不安是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火車切廣光和鉋切長光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓你這小丫頭拿上  草壁流也墮落了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅  這傢伙是個可怕的高手  拜託你支援了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劫之眼的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手我另有安排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打倒過的黑騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯佩爾比亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  草壁操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  草壁一族最強的天才術士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成黑騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了抵抗毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  為了保護我的阿瓦利提亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁操
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧為傳說中的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間察覺力量之差而選擇退守  值得誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有改變戰術也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有換命的覺悟  我也不敢輕易出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的這條命  全為朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何  存在於此？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等強大的氣息…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅是沒法幫我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理為什麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子也還沒有回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有這力量  我被父母遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是彩子她  將我撫養至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直撫養至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本是廢柴一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦沒了彩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會瘋掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這樣的彩子  卻被你給…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再這樣了  那不是黑騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是幻影而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻已經  制止不了我自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已然控制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這曾讓我父母懼怕過的  也是我所懼怕著的破壞衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這炎魔的暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快  我就會喪失掉自我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣  賢久前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能死在你的手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心滿意足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然同時操縱著  兩個法陣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小栞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等  等著驅君他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為驅君他叫我待在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的話  正在外面跟黑騎士戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開  小栞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你要妨礙他進一步的成長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得讓你睡上一會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護驅君  我必須得去救驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的他  已經能夠自保了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是絕對不會輸給那種人偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君他  沒問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那樣的話  我不去也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過其他幾個  我就不能保證他們是否平安了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了啦  只要驅君沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  小栞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝口茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去泡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的  你的攻擊已經被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是像這樣消耗下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連同歸於盡都危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君和我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在同一所孤兒院裡長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時候起  驅君他就一直很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便成了我如今的父母的養女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君他後來也開始一個人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並和我進了同一所高中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和驅君  一直都是在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是  以後也肯定會一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡童話式的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「從那之後  兩人便在一起  過上了幸福的生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這點能耐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前  我多多少少還抱有些期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可現在看來  草壁流也是命數將盡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需一瞬間便好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找到哪怕是瞬息即逝的破綻…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:19:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身破敵  並請同除災厄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如神隱十拳  炎靈孕生  火車且來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送諸焰羅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一擊  將賭上我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火天墜衝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火…  火車切長光竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子  喝了草壁家的血是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  「為了朋友和明日」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之間的這層羈絆  已然斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁書目錄處察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這綾女之丘之上  有著邪惡的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是便派我前來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  禁書目錄處是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了銷毀或封印會給這個世界造成災難的一切魔術而創設的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界規模最大的魔術機關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術機關？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  栞同學就是魔術師…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成黑騎士也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不單單是魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是從前禁書目錄處所派出的使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了消滅惡魔而戰的一群人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是說  黑騎士他們是正義的使者？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於斯佩爾比亞  我想美鈴同學應該更為清楚才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天壤…之別…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全及不上她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鈴前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了賢久前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.92,0:24:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢久死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.25,0:24:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「為了朋友和明日」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之間的這層羈絆  已然斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.32,0:24:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.53,0:24:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.50,0:24:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得  在惡夢的盡頭  真會有答案嗎
